{"tid":1901712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[商台？港台？]約十人到港台抗議《頭條新聞》　要求梁家榮道歉辭職","createTime":"2020-02-28T03:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T13:48:27.000Z","uid":111460,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0f3ce643d729a6b3685d951a0829c8e55bad30","tid":1901712,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511399-20200228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511399-20200228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0S3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=abb901c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511399-20200228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cb5ef9eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511399-20200228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n大約10人早上到香港電台抗議，批評港台早前播出的一輯《頭條新聞》內容，要求廣播處長梁家榮公開道歉及辭職，又指責商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華監管不力，要求他下台。<br />\n<br />\n到港台抗議的人士質疑港台為政府喉舌，應準確持正報道，但就違反港台約章，撕裂社會，抹黑警隊的抗疫貢獻。亦有人批評《頭條新聞》歪曲事實，說兩名主持不正經做節目，質疑港台為何以往可解聘主持人李慧玲，但現時不解聘兩名主持人。<span style=\"color: red;\">李慧玲實為商業電台前節目主持，2014年被商業電台中止合約。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，現場人士亦唱歌，諷刺「壹傳媒」創辦人黎智英被捕，港台派人接收請願信，他們逗留約15分鐘後離開。<br />\n<br />\n係咪之前搞錯商台同RTHK班友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107a1ae5b12156ef1c88d302be9bec7414d5460a","tid":1901712,"uid":59460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"上次好似去錯商台示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61de6465f9cf49e548f31780669fa4a444df5550","tid":1901712,"uid":56819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"十慢人好心就收皮啦,肉唔肉酸呀?"}]}